Package gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HealthBar
    Represents the character healthbar as an imageicon overlayed over another one.
    Images
    Images class which represents the manager and database for images.
    Level
    Level class which represents the level in which the user will be playing on.
    Map
    The Map class uses a 2D array to represent the level map that is generated in each room.
    Room
    Room class which represents the room in which the enemies and user are currently present in.
    ScoreBoard
    Represents character scoreboard
    Tile
    represents a tile within the map
    Top
    Represents top menu bar of game
    Torch
    represents a wall torch
    TorchThread
    thread to manage torches
